tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE fashion_photography_services (
    client_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    client_name VARCHAR(50),
    preferences TEXT,
    feedback TEXT,
    past_orders TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Feedback (
  feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  client_id UUID,
  rating INT,
  comments TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (client_id) REFERENCES ClientPreferences(client_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  client_id INT,
  rating INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_date DATE,
  FOREIGN KEY (client_id) REFERENCES ClientPreferences(client_id)
);

CREATE TABLE PastOrders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  client_id INT,
  order_date DATE,
  service_type VARCHAR(50),
  order_total DECIMAL(10, 2),
  FOREIGN KEY (client_id) REFERENCES ClientPreferences(client_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ClientOrders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  client_id INT,
  photographer_id INT,
  order_date DATE,
  service_type VARCHAR(50),
  order_total DECIMAL(10, 2),
  FOREIGN KEY (client_id) REFERENCES ClientPreferences(client_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (photographer_id) REFERENCES Photographer(photographer_id)
);
